      "rationale": "Nonlinear static analyses used a Newton-Raphson scheme with residual convergence criterion of 1e-6. Energy balance was verified at each converged increment. No divergence or excessive iteration counts were observed across the 11-construct ensemble."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
