      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst review of model setup; checklist completed and archived.",
      "rationale": "A second analyst independently reviewed boundary conditions, material assignments, contact definitions, and load application against the documented modeling protocol. All checklist items were resolved prior to production runs. No use errors were identified."
