      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model inputs match test specimen measurements to within measurement uncertainty; documented traceability between coupon data and FEA inputs.",
      "rationale": "Material property inputs to each of the 11 FEA replicates were matched to the corresponding specimen's lot coupon data. Geometric inputs were matched to CMM measurements of each specimen. Traceability matrix linking specimen ID to FEA input file is archived. Equivalency is established."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric; acceptance threshold E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% for all QoIs.",
      "rationale": "E/uval was computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement across all 11 constructs and both laboratories. All three QoIs satisfied E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10%. Graphical overlays of force-displacement curves confirm qualitative agreement. Output comparison criterion is met."
    },
    {
