      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly support the regulatory claim that the non-cannulated design meets structural performance requirements. The QoIs are clinically relevant surrogates for fatigue and fracture risk. Relevance is fully established."
