    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the conservative acceptance bounds applied to the output comparison and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. The overall evidence package is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level determination for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU.",
